- ğŸ“± **Responsive Design** - Works seamlessly on desktop and mobile devices
- ğŸ­ **Artist Profiles** - View detailed artist information and their top tracks
- ğŸ’¿ **Album Views** - Browse complete album tracklists
- ğŸ“» **Podcast Support** - Discover and listen to podcasts
